Package: blueskynet
Title: Analyze and Visualize Networks on Bluesky Social
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Lasse", "Hjorth Madsen", , "lassehjorthmadsen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides comprehensive tools for collecting, analyzing, and
    visualizing social networks from Bluesky Social <https://bsky.app>.
    Enables users to authenticate with the Bluesky API, collect follower
    networks, perform community detection, calculate network metrics, and
    create interactive 3D visualizations. Includes functions for network
    expansion algorithms, text analysis of user profiles, and follow/unfollow
    management. Designed for social network researchers, data scientists, and
    anyone interested in understanding social structures on Bluesky Social.
